<title>About -ZppixBot</title>
<h1>About</h1>
<body>
ZppixBot is an IRC bot running <a href="https://sopel.chat">Sopel</a> 6.5.1 and Python 2.7.9. ZppixBot has lots of commands and more can be added by writing more modules. The home channel for ZppixBot is <a href="irc://chat.freenode.net/#ZppixBot">#ZppixBot</a>where you can get help from the maintainers. ZppixBot's current maintainers are Zppix and Reception123.</body>